# MusicBrainz reads need NO credentials — the search/lookup/browse/cover-art
# tools work out of the box. Optionally override the User-Agent:
# MUSICBRAINZ_USER_AGENT=my-app/1.0 ( me@example.com )

# OAuth — ONLY for the write tools (submit_tags / submit_rating /
# modify_collection). Register an application at
# https://musicbrainz.org/account/applications (redirect URI
# urn:ietf:wg:oauth:2.0:oob), complete the OAuth flow with the
# tag+rating+collection scopes to obtain a refresh token, then set:
# MUSICBRAINZ_OAUTH_CLIENT_ID=your_client_id
# MUSICBRAINZ_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET=your_client_secret
# MUSICBRAINZ_OAUTH_REFRESH_TOKEN=your_refresh_token
